title: Elizabeth Bathory: The Blood Countess
description:
Former FBI agent and criminal profiler Candice DeLong explores the life of Countess Elizabeth Bathory, also known as the Blood Countess. The Countess was accused of torturing and killing over 600 women, making her one of the most prolific female serial killers of all time.
